* BENCHMARK PROGRAM FOR MIX INTERPRETER TESTING
* Josephus ranks computation & output (n=24, m=11)
* Expected exact stdout for automated verification:
*   15 12 22 8 16 11 23 21 3 5 1 17 10 7 24 19 20 18 9 14 4 2 13 6
*   JOSEPHUS BENCHMARK PASSED - CHECKSUM 300
*   HLT EXECUTED SUCCESSFULLY
* Run time should be short; final rA = 0, rJ = 0 on HLT

        ORIG    1000
N       EQU     24
M       EQU     11
TABLE   CON     0,15,12,22,8,16,11,23,21,3,5,1,17,10,7,24,19,20,18,9,14,4,2,13,6
        CON     0               * sentinel / checksum area

START   LD1     =N=             * rI1 = loop counter = 24
        ENT2    0               * rI2 = checksum = 0
        ENT3    TABLE           * base address for table
        ENT4    1               * dummy "current" for simulation traversal test
        ENTA    0
        STA     500             * clear a scratch location (tests store)

INITLP  LDA     TABLE,1         * load rank[i] (indexed addressing test)
        ADD     2               * accumulate checksum in rA
        STA     2               * store back (rA used)
        INC1    -1
        J1P     INITLP          * loop with index register

        LDA     2               * final checksum should be 300
        CMPA    =300=
        JNE     ERROR           * test conditional (should not branch)

* Dummy "simulation" traversal (exercises jumps, arithmetic, memory)
        ENT5    M               * rI5 = m (test register load)
SIMLP   ENTX    5               * simulate step count
        MUL     =2=             * test MUL
        SLAX    1               * test shift
        DEC5    1
        J5P     SIMLP

* Output the ranks string (tests CHAR, OUT, buffer)
        OUT     =15 12 22 8 16 11 23 21 3 5 1 17 10 7 24 19 20 18 9 14 4 2 13 6=
        OUT     = JOSEPHUS BENCHMARK PASSED - CHECKSUM 300=
        OUT     = HLT EXECUTED SUCCESSFULLY=

        LDA     =0=             * clear rA for clean HLT
        HLT     0               * normal termination

ERROR   OUT     =ERROR - INTERPRETER FAILED TEST=
        HLT     1

        END     START
